{
  "stem": "11144.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one day, somebody-- the Russian people, the Ukranian people that we lived with-- tipped my parents off that the Russians are coming, and that they are taking all the refugees and sending them to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my parents-- now, this I was told.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember this incident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they jumped out the windows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they hid in the back of the building in a, like-- what do you call it, where the horses-- in a stable.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they left the two of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Me and my sister, they left home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Russians really came in and asked for my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people said they didn't know where they were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they wanted to take me and my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people stood up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, over their dead bodies, which was really very brave of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't know the-- They were Ukrainian?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know the Russians at that time yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they could have been shot right then and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they told them they were not going to give the children away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They should come back and, and take the whole family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she, she wasn't giving the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they, they left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after that-- my cousin, also, that we took with us from Radom was with us up to that point.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, she told me later on that, from then on, she left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because she came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she didn't find us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So apparently, right after my, my parents came back, they found out about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to pack and leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they were afraid that my parents were going to be-- that we are going to be taken, which maybe would have been better.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe my father would have lived if they took us to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
